        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 22. Pleurotoma inchoata Sturany, 1900, Station 145 (Dahlak Archipelago, Eritrea, Red Sea). A. Original figure by Sturany (1903). B-D, F. Holotype, NHMW 84251: front (B), right side (C), back (D), protoconch (F). E. Original holotype label. Scale bars: B-D: 5 mm, F: 0.5 mm." ;
